<h1>History of Zaza's Beauty Salon</h1>
<h2>In 2014,I went to school and studied Cosmetology Short Skills Course In GEL NAIL EXTENTIONS at Northlink College in Cape Town Bellville Campus.</h2>

<h2>After completing the course and extensive research into the nail industry, I brought back cutting-edge techniques.I called my friends and family to do their nails.</h2>

<h2>Keeping up with market and consumer trends has been at the forefront of Zaza's Beauty Salon for a year and this passion has allowed the group to reinvent itself over this year . These customers know that when visiting Zaza's Beauty Salon you can expect high quality nail enhancements and beauty services, by fully trained and knowledgeable staff.</h2>

